		<title>2024 Presidential Election: How Trump or Harris&#8217;s Victory Could Shape Financial Markets and Create Trading Opportunities</title>
		<link>https://www.atfx.com/en/analysis/trading-strategies/trump-vs-harris-election-market-impact-2024</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[ATFX]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 07:00:54 +0000</pubDate>
